00:09:53,520 --> 00:10:00,760
Tom, how are you?
汤姆，你好吗？

250
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:03,320
Hey, we missed you at the party last night.
嘿，我们昨晚在派对上没见到你。

251
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,320
Are you okay?
你没事吧？

252
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,960
