我不知道。

253
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,760
I didn't really feel like going out.
我真的不太想出门。

254
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:10,360
I guess I'm feeling a little homesick.
我想我有点想家了。

255
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,360
Come on.
别这样。

256
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,360
We've been through this already.
我们之前已经经历过这个了。

257
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:15,920
Look, I know the adjustment was hard when you first got here.
听着，我知道你刚来的时候适应起来很难。

258
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:18,800
But we agree that you're going to try and deal with it.
但我们说好你会努力应对的。

259
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:19,960
I was.
我确实在努力。

260
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:24,000
It's just that the holidays are coming up and I won't be able to go home because I can't
只是假期快到了，我回不了家，因为我付不起

