在厄瓜多尔我们通常有更独特的传统。

303
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,000
So it's very fun.
所以很有趣。

304
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:31,520
The family gets together, we dance, we eat.
家人聚在一起，我们跳舞、吃饭。

305
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:36,200
So but yeah, I've been away from home so long that I rarely get homesick anymore.
但嗯，我离家太久了，所以很少再想家了。

306
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,400
But it's great to go back and spend time with the family.
但回去和家人团聚还是很棒的。

307
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:43,560
So after my visit to Ecuador, then I might get homesick for a little while, but then
所以在我回厄瓜多尔之后，我可能会短暂地想家，但然后

308
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:44,560
it goes away.
这种感觉就消失了。

309
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,560
Yeah.
嗯。

310
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:46,800
